description:
This video was made possible thanks to everyone on the Simple History Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/simplehistory

Europe has been obsessed with Ancient Egypt for over 2,000 years — from Roman emperors parading obelisks, to Renaissance scholars chasing hidden wisdom, to Napoleon’s grand expedition and the discovery of Tutankhamun. This video explores the rise of Egyptomania: the fascination, the myths, the plundering, the mystery, and Egypt’s ultimate reclaiming of its ancient past.
